{
  "stem": "1873.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it so happened that, one evening, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a Jewish policeman had come in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody in this room should go out and should go outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Outside was a little yard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And across the yard was a prosektorium, a place where they keep the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people kept-- stood up from the bed and they-- And it was January 8, 1943.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This date I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- so I stood up, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had a bad feeling, but I was very-- really, very sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was moving slowly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, I went outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now, I don't remember why I did turn around and did go back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It could be two reasons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First of all, when I stepped, with my bare feet on the snow, it was like burning, like a hot iron.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All because I notice, next to another little house outside, I notice SS soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, I turn around, went back, and hide under the bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] About five minutes later, a Jewish policeman did come in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I, laying under the bed, look for what I see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I see this Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I said, hello, hello, to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He noticed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, ah, how did you stay?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did you-- did they let you stay here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, OK, so don't worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hide.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You will hear some shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But don't be scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a few minutes later, I heard screaming, shooting from the-- from the nearby house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish policeman didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- and I was under this bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
